/ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/164485/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 'Cabazitaxel, Paclitaxel, Teniposide, Irinotecan, Etoposide, Docetaxel', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 1767369485);
